Class RecentSquaresFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, InSquareProfile.InSquareProfileListener

    public class RecentSquaresFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
implements InSquareProfile.InSquareProfileListener
    This fragment show the recent squares used by the user. The recent squares are those in which he wrote at least a message
